What are you thinking so seriously about?

67
00:04:39,867 --> 00:04:41,267
Oh,

68
00:04:41,267 --> 00:04:42,633
you were writing?

69
00:04:42,633 --> 00:04:44,267
Sorry.

70
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:48,533
