71
00:04:51,233 --> 00:04:53,367
[Trip Selection Team]

72
00:04:53,367 --> 00:04:55,533
This isn't an exclusive.

73
00:04:55,533 --> 00:04:57,867
- Mr. O.
- You were bragging that

74
00:04:57,867 --> 00:04:59,600
our Yeo Reum was doing a solo travel show,

75
